"&lt;/toolbars&gt;\n"
"&lt;/qconfig&gt;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to get more information"
msgstr "Kako dobiti više informacija"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other &calligra; manuals"
msgstr "Drugi priručnici za &calligra;u"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For detailed information on the different &calligra; applications, please "
"consult their respective manuals."
msgstr ""
"Za detaljnije informacije raznih &calligra; aplikacija, pogledajte u "
"zvanične priručnike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Links"
msgstr "Linkovi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following links should be useful if you're looking for more information "
"about &kde; or &calligra;."
msgstr ""
"Sljedeći linkovi mogu biti korisni ako tražite više inforacija o &kde; ili "
"&calligra;i."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://calligra.org\">The &calligra; homepage</ulink>. Here you "
"can find information on how to get and install &calligra;, news about "
"&calligra; development, screenshots &etc;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://calligra.org\"> &calligra; stranica</ulink>. Ovdje "
"možete pronaći informacije o tome kako nabaviti i instalirati &calligra;u, "
"novosti o razvoju &calligra;e, primjere i sl."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.kde.org\">The &kde; Homepage</ulink>. &kde; is the "
"most advanced and absolutely free desktop environment for unix-like "
"operating systems. &calligra; makes use of the &kde; libraries."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.kde.org\"> &kde; Stranica </ulink>. &kde; je "
"najnaprednije i potpuno besplatno Desktop okruženje za unix-tip operativne "
"sisteme. &calligra; koristi &kde; biblioteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://qt-project.org/\">&Qt; page</ulink>. The creators of the "
"C++-toolkit &Qt;. &kde; and &calligra; make use of &Qt;."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://qt-project.org/\">&Qt; stranica</ulink>. Kreatori C++.a, "
"&kde; i &calligra; koriste &Qt;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "Programming &calligra;"
msgstr "Programiranje &calligra;e"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to do &calligra; development, the following resources might be "
"of interest:"
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da razvijate &calligra;, sljedeći izvori mogu biti od pomoći:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At <ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde.org/Development\">http://techbase.kde."
"org/Development</ulink> you'll find many documents about programming with "
"&Qt; and &kde;. You can find the online version of the complete &kde; "
"library documentation on <ulink url=\"http://api.kde.org/\">KDE API "
"Reference</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Na stranici:  <ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde.org/Development\">http://"
"techbase.kde.org/Development</ulink> ćete naći mnogo dokumenata o "
"programiranju &Qt; i &kde;. Možete naći online verzije potpune &kde; "
"dokumentacije na linku:  <ulink url=\"http://api.kde.org/\">KDE API "
"Reference</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first step for contributing code is to follow <ulink url=\"http://"
"community.kde.org/Calligra/Building/Building_Calligra\">those instructions</"
"ulink> to get the source code and build it."
msgstr ""
"Da biste doprinijeli programskom kodu, prvi korak je da slijedite <ulink url="
"\"http://community.kde.org/Calligra/Building/Building_Calligra\">ove "
"insrukcije</ulink> da biste dobili izvorni kod i doradili ga."

